a.n: World Grand Prix Fight TNA, 1/8th finals, TATNEFT CUP, Tatneft Arena, Kazan, Russia

p.d: The second stage of the 1/8th finals of the "TATNEFT CUP" tournament, which will take place in Kazan (Russia), at the "Tatneft Arena" in Ice Sports Palace. Six events are scheduled for the event in three weight categories involving fighters from all over the world.
